Apache-2.0

### Type-checking

```bash
pip install mypy
mypy --strict .
```

The included mypy.ini restricts analysis to the src/ tree and skips
build/, dist/, virtual-env and egg directories so duplicate-module
errors do not occur even if you build wheels locally.
